window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's Christmastime at Marlow House Bed and Breakfast, and Danielle has a full house. When a woman, stranded far from home, shows up on the doorstep and begs for a room for the night, how can Danielle tell her the inn is full and turn her away? </p> <p>After all, it's almost Christmas. </p> <p>The woman makes quite an impression on the other guests, especially when she mysteriously disappears. Is it foul play - or something supernatural? </p>"; 
